                  "snippet": "Latte: Espresso combined with steamed milk and topped with a light layer of foam."
                },
                {
                  "snippet": "Americano: Espresso diluted with hot water for a smooth, black coffee profile."
                },
                {
                  "snippet": "Cold Brew: Coffee grounds steeped in cold water over many hours, resulting in a smooth, low-acidity, and highly caffeinated drink ."
